high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to face the black table
Pick up the cup from the center of the table
Turn around and go to the stove
Place the cup inside the microwave above the stove, turn the microwave on for a few seconds, and take out the cup
Take the cup  and go to the right to the sink
Put the cup inside the cabinet above the sink
anns.task_desc: To place a heated cup inside a cabinet

high_descs: walk to face round black table
pick up black glass on left on table
heat glass in microwave, pick up glass from microwave
turn to face cabinet above sink
put glass in cabinet above sink
anns.task_desc: put heated glass away in kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter, turn right, move to the round black table.
Pick up the cup in the middle of the table.
Turn around, bring the cup to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Take the heated cup to the sink on the right of the microwave.
Put the heated cup in the cabinet above the sink in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup away in a cabinet over the sink.
